@node features " Features "

Features of BrickFast 1.00:

- you can choose between 3 level sets 
	and more come soon...
- multiball option
- fire, brickthrough
- cheats <- only in the registered version!
- ball saving guard
- many falling objects
- nice graphics and animations
- amazing sound effects and musics
- you can push the table by pressing the spacebar to
	  modify the path of the balls in every 10 minutes 
- you can quit anytime you want by pressing the ESC
- press 'P' during the game to pause
- to turn on/off the music press the 'M' during the game

You have to register to be able to switch the cheats on!

Cheat keys:

Press 'N' to warp to the  next level.
Use the button '1' to slow down the ball and press '2'
to make the ball faster.
Press 'G' to activate the guard and 'H' to deactivate it.
Pressing '1', 'G' or the 'N' button will void your
high scores.
@endnode

@node tips " Tips & Tricks "

Some tips & tricks:

	- You can aim and release the ball by pressing
	   the left or the right mousebutton when it is locked
	   to the bat.
	- You can get power ups when you hit a brick with your
	   original grey ball. The green ball won't give you
	   any power up.
	- You won't get power ups by shooting down the bricks. 
	- The guard is activated immediately as you pick up
	   the falling guard power up object and deactivated 
	   as it disappears (the time is out).
	- There are black bricks!
	- You have to hit some bricks many times to destroy them.
	- Collect as much money as possible to get an extra life!
	- There aren't negative 'power ups' such as death or
	   ball speed-up so you can collect as many as possible.
	- Using the space will cost you 50 points each time.
	- You are allowed to push the table every 20 second.
	- You can accelerate the ball by pressing '2' without
	   voiding your score. Pressing the 'H' - guard off
	   also won't void your score.
	- Press the ESC to quit or 'P' to pause the game.

@endnode

