@node install " Installation of BrickFast"

	Installation:

Just unarchive BrickFast among your favourite games,
an start the game clicking on its icon.

	Registration:

To register the game double click on the registry icon
and then enter your registry number.
The program will create your personal keyfile for the
game.

	Uninstallation:

Uninstallation is easy. Just delete the BrickFast drawer. 
No other junks left on the HD. 
@endnode

