@node hard "Hardware required."

		Hardware requirements:

The required hardware is any Amiga with at least 900KB of free 
CHIP RAM and 2MB of FAST RAM.
AGA is not neccesary but a hard disk is required to install
the game.

To run BrickFast at full speed (50fps) we recommend using
68030/50 turbo and 4 Mb FAST RAM or better.

The game works under UAE, but extremely slowly on a P166.
@endnode
